
# Necessary elements:
# Variables, Domains Constraints.
# The variables are the boxes of the grid.
# The domains are the values that each box can be assigned, namely 1 to n in an n x n grid.
# The constraints:
# Only a single instance of a value can appear in any column of the grid.
# Only a single instance of a value can appear in any row of the grid.
# [TENTATIVE] Only a single instance of a value can appear diagonally in the grid. This might be 
# limited to only the diagonals starting from the corners of the grid.
